{"tid":301412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拍埋片]劉曉波獄中片段突然曝光　疑支那官方放出　欲證善待並無耽誤治療","createTime":"2017-06-28T15:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T03:54:33.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"945b6adc0410db7004904d52234b47c04ef528cd","tid":301412,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"Youtube頻道「博訊直擊」今晚發佈「劉曉波在獄中視頻曝光」3分鐘片段，並注明「應該是官方特意放出」，首次顯示劉曉波在遼寧錦州監獄的生活，以及在擬似病房接受治療的情況，劉曉波接受各種身體檢查及醫生診斷的部份，佔去片段大部份時間，並配上字幕介紹，也有劉曉波向着鏡頭說出感激戴隊長及靳隊長的關心他的健康。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉波患末期肝癌、獲保外就醫的消息本周一曝光後，有維權人士和海外輿論質疑獄方隱瞞劉曉波病情，耽誤劉的治療，使到劉陷入末期癌病的嚴重境況。今次這段明顯由獄方拍攝的片段突然在網絡流出，外界普遍相信是大陸官方刻意放出，意圖反駁指責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ekSylSqrXpU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DekSylSqrXpU&d=%2Fjn%2FRJCpn5RZyrCIhlXUMviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ddfa3cb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ekSylSqrXpU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共醒過肥仔金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b89da339082b282aa114cf9c2ae9678e5910085","tid":301412,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"以為拍條濕尻片就有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f674702057ba5cfa800b8f342591fc287d8d36","tid":301412,"uid":57705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:34:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dae39f66fef20b066147ba8588b938c015d74437","tid":301412,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T00:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5de47dd1850dabcdba6cd3feda1ba6d65fa8493","tid":301412,"uid":11001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:16:20.000Z","msg":"戴眼鏡做MRI <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hk